Package: odvis
Title: Parameterising ggplot2 Graphics for Origin-Destination Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Roger", "Beecham", , "r.j.beecham@leeds.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8563-7251"))
Maintainer: Roger Beecham <r.j.beecham@leeds.ac.uk>
Description: Creates origin-destination graphics using 'ggplot2'. You provide the origin-destination data and 'odvis' (plus a complimentary package, 'gridmappr') provides functions that transform data such that it can be used by 'ggplot2' to generate flow-lines and matrix-based origin-destination visualizations. 
Imports: 
    magrittr,
    tibble
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    testthat
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
